%F A394072 Equals (7/2)*(cot(Pi/7) + sqrt(3)) = (7/2)*(A178818  + A002194).
%F A394072 Equals the largest root of x^12 - 343*x^10 + 38416*x^8 - 1798349*x^6 + 35412349*x^4 - 242121642*x^2 + 282475249.
